{"tid":2439465,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「長髮公主」真人版　她一頭秀髮竟15年未剪已長得比人還高","createTime":"2021-03-09T09:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T10:23:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"416adec541e4370abb11ded2f779e84b9421fc60","tid":2439465,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:28:16.000Z","msg":"這真的是「長髮公主」真人版！出身日本東京的Rin Kambe，一頭長髮15年未剪，已經長到190公分，比一般人的身高還長！<br />\n<br />\n《每日郵報》報導，目前從事模特兒和舞者工作的Rin Kambe，現年35歲，身高167公分，她說從20歲開始，就未曾再剪過頭髮，現在頭髮已長得比她身高還長。<br />\n<br />\nRin Kambe表示，從小她的父母就管教嚴格，小時候不但不准留長髮，還因為踢足球，都把頭髮剪得很短，但20歲之後，為了展現自我，就不曾再剪髮，現在這一頭長髮，反而成了她的特色，也是代表她自信的「武器」。<br />\n<br />\n「有很多人問我的頭髮是真的還假的？有人很欣賞，也有人覺得像妖怪，但我尊重不同的看法，不過我覺得這是亞洲之美。」但Rin Kambe也坦承，頭髮這麼長，經常會造成生活上的困擾，像是換衣服時就很不方便，洗頭時也很麻煩，但她還是非常寶貝她的頭髮，不僅每天護髮，還要擦頭皮霜，以確保頭皮有足夠養分讓頭髮繼續生長，而且保持烏黑亮麗。(即時新聞中心／綜合報導)<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/iOGWbfgMWg1l7wyzpyn0wZPwBtE=/760x906/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7VYSRCPYMFAX7N2FVK4B3TNFBQ.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiOGWbfgMWg1l7wyzpyn0wZPwBtE%3D%2F760x906%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7VYSRCPYMFAX7N2FVK4B3TNFBQ.PNG&h=533733bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210309/H6BEYD4S5JBJTCVSJXCFCNDHOQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210309%2FH6BEYD4S5JBJTCVSJXCFCNDHOQ%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy6ZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=98208a61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210309%2FH6BEYD4S5JBJTCVSJXCFCNDHOQ%2F&h=4a63db74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210309/H6BEYD4S5JBJTCVSJXCFCNDHOQ/</a>"},{"pid":"97349486a85cbb550408de212c1ca820cd127d1a","tid":2439465,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":